description: Search experts say the reported sighting of a plane in difficulty could have been a parachute flare.
title: No evidence of suspected Sark plane crash found after search
title_page: No evidence of suspected Sark plane crash found after search - BBC News
maintext: Chief Officer of Channel Islands Airsearch, John Fitzgerald, said it was unlikely to have been a plane, as there was no evidence of any oil on the water.
